  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328700/extras/72e3ea4bd30bf62ad2648a74fe840e03.poster.avif?t=1753365374\" width=800 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328700/extras/72e3ea4bd30bf62ad2648a74fe840e03.webm?t=1753365374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328700/extras/72e3ea4bd30bf62ad2648a74fe840e03.mp4?t=1753365374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>3D Escape Game: Chinese Room</strong> is a Chinese-style escape room game. You’ll find yourself in a variety of mysterious, challenging rooms inspired by Chinese culture, where you’ll uncover secrets and solve puzzles.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Beauty of Eastern Zen</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each scene pays homage to traditional Chinese Zen aesthetics, with serene lighting, minimalist lines, and gentle colors. This design enhances the puzzle-solving process, creating a tranquil, focused experience. We aim to visually convey a Zen ambiance, immersing you in a peaceful, ancient Chinese courtyard, where you can savor the unique cultural charm.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328700/extras/aa4a2b96d2e3771035a39ce649b563a0.poster.avif?t=1753365374\" width=800 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328700/extras/aa4a2b96d2e3771035a39ce649b563a0.webm?t=1753365374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328700/extras/aa4a2b96d2e3771035a39ce649b563a0.mp4?t=1753365374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Exquisite 3D Graphics</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Through detailed textures, soft lighting, and realistic physics, we strive to provide a visually captivating experience that deepens immersion. From carved stone details to lattice window designs, every element reveals a meticulous attention to detail, transporting you to an authentic ancient Chinese world.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328700/extras/7ddb7db46da8aa6e22562281f6451366.poster.avif?t=1753365374\" width=800 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328700/extras/7ddb7db46da8aa6e22562281f6451366.webm?t=1753365374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328700/extras/7ddb7db46da8aa6e22562281f6451366.mp4?t=1753365374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Balanced Puzzle Design</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Throughout the game, you’ll encounter a series of classic puzzles and mini-games. Neither too simple nor too overwhelming, the difficulty is carefully calibrated to offer a sense of achievement and the joy of exploration as you work your way through each challenge.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328700/extras/6a81043341e742e7a96ba9e0e55db678.poster.avif?t=1753365374\" width=800 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328700/extras/6a81043341e742e7a96ba9e0e55db678.webm?t=1753365374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328700/extras/6a81043341e742e7a96ba9e0e55db678.mp4?t=1753365374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328700/extras/72e3ea4bd30bf62ad2648a74fe840e03.poster.avif?t=1753365374\" width=800 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328700/extras/72e3ea4bd30bf62ad2648a74fe840e03.webm?t=1753365374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328700/extras/72e3ea4bd30bf62ad2648a74fe840e03.mp4?t=1753365374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>3D Escape Game: Chinese Room</strong> is a Chinese-style escape room game. You’ll find yourself in a variety of mysterious, challenging rooms inspired by Chinese culture, where you’ll uncover secrets and solve puzzles.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Beauty of Eastern Zen</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each scene pays homage to traditional Chinese Zen aesthetics, with serene lighting, minimalist lines, and gentle colors. This design enhances the puzzle-solving process, creating a tranquil, focused experience. We aim to visually convey a Zen ambiance, immersing you in a peaceful, ancient Chinese courtyard, where you can savor the unique cultural charm.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328700/extras/aa4a2b96d2e3771035a39ce649b563a0.poster.avif?t=1753365374\" width=800 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328700/extras/aa4a2b96d2e3771035a39ce649b563a0.webm?t=1753365374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328700/extras/aa4a2b96d2e3771035a39ce649b563a0.mp4?t=1753365374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Exquisite 3D Graphics</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Through detailed textures, soft lighting, and realistic physics, we strive to provide a visually captivating experience that deepens immersion. From carved stone details to lattice window designs, every element reveals a meticulous attention to detail, transporting you to an authentic ancient Chinese world.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328700/extras/7ddb7db46da8aa6e22562281f6451366.poster.avif?t=1753365374\" width=800 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328700/extras/7ddb7db46da8aa6e22562281f6451366.webm?t=1753365374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328700/extras/7ddb7db46da8aa6e22562281f6451366.mp4?t=1753365374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Balanced Puzzle Design</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Throughout the game, you’ll encounter a series of classic puzzles and mini-games. Neither too simple nor too overwhelming, the difficulty is carefully calibrated to offer a sense of achievement and the joy of exploration as you work your way through each challenge.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328700/extras/6a81043341e742e7a96ba9e0e55db678.poster.avif?t=1753365374\" width=800 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328700/extras/6a81043341e742e7a96ba9e0e55db678.webm?t=1753365374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328700/extras/6a81043341e742e7a96ba9e0e55db678.mp4?t=1753365374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
